    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731290/extras/c92ba8a411dae29f09aa4a5320b94de5.avif?t=1771414736\" width=616 height=98 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731290/extras/6503ad2ba333dd7a73989b9c233fe662.poster.avif?t=1771414736\" width=600 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731290/extras/6503ad2ba333dd7a73989b9c233fe662.webm?t=1771414736\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731290/extras/6503ad2ba333dd7a73989b9c233fe662.mp4?t=1771414736\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>我们设计的特殊战斗镜头将让你仿佛置身电影之中。你不只是在玩游戏，更是在观赏一部动作大片！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731290/extras/9a516e0f8572bece2af98e0df0b22a86.avif?t=1771414736\" width=616 height=96 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731290/extras/d0453ec26c5bce3b6d5993648ab91ab1.poster.avif?t=1771414736\" width=600 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731290/extras/d0453ec26c5bce3b6d5993648ab91ab1.webm?t=1771414736\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731290/extras/d0453ec26c5bce3b6d5993648ab91ab1.mp4?t=1771414736\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>倾享电影级枪战与Freeflow清版动作游戏的激情融合，深入《SPINE》战斗的混沌热潮。一招一式都是枪焰与贴身弹雨夹缝中的一场舞蹈。这不只是一款游戏；它更是一张空白的画布，静待你留下自己饱含毁灭之美的笔触。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731290/extras/54de1d0d8a99c425cfc7c5bc6b7faa54.avif?t=1771414736\" width=616 height=96 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731290/extras/6cb44b32fb32674c5f6b919c699eb25b.poster.avif?t=1771414736\" width=600 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731290/extras/6cb44b32fb32674c5f6b919c699eb25b.webm?t=1771414736\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731290/extras/6cb44b32fb32674c5f6b919c699eb25b.mp4?t=1771414736\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>踏入迷人的赛博朋克世界，走进写满凌厉激斗的故事。穿行于乌托邦闪亮的假面之间，探索肮脏腐朽的暗巷，在各个地点展开令人肾上腺素飙升的枪火大战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731290/extras/31a1f85ed9371b870cf44c571e1d0e90.avif?t=1771414736\" width=616 height=96 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731290/extras/20551945be8d0c248b50bee24ac0a296.poster.avif?t=1771414736\" width=600 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731290/extras/20551945be8d0c248b50bee24ac0a296.webm?t=1771414736\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731290/extras/20551945be8d0c248b50bee24ac0a296.mp4?t=1771414736\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>与叛逆街头艺术家“赤线”和她的战斗AI伙伴“源脊”——一款拥有自我意识的战斗植入物——一同迈入近未来世界，走上一段无畏之旅。与他们携手对抗AI的压迫政权，用一场场战斗在走过的街道上激起涟漪，改变自己相识之人的生活。</p>",
